overview: The user wanted to improve the aesthetics of their sleep questionnaire
  app, which they felt was functional but lacked visual appeal. The agent
  conducted a thorough review of the app's styling, identifying areas like the
  generic color palette, plain backgrounds, and basic form elements as needing
  improvement. The approach involved implementing a new, calming sleep-themed
  color palette with deep indigo/purple and teal accents. Key components like
  the QuestionnaireForm, IntroSection, Progress bar, Slider, CheckboxField,
  RadioGroupField, and ReportSection were updated with refined styling, better
  visual hierarchy, and more inviting designs. The outcome is a more
  professional, visually appealing, and emotionally resonant interface tailored
  for a sleep assessment experience.
